      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2) must hold a current FDA-recognized software quality assurance certification or equivalent documented QMS. Version control and audit trail of simulation scripts required.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2 is operated under an ISO 9001:2015-certified QMS. All simulation input decks and post-processing scripts are version-controlled in Git (tag: morrison-cpb-v3.2). Automated regression test suite (187 unit tests) passes at each release. SQA documentation package on file. Gradation 2 requirement met."
