      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations via benchmark problems with known analytical solutions. Order-of-accuracy confirmation required for at least one canonical flow.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent code verification documented against the ASME V&V 20 lid-driven cavity and Poiseuille flow benchmarks. Observed order of accuracy p = 1.97 (expected: 2nd order), confirming correct discretization. Manufacturer verification report (Fluent VVR-2022) reviewed and accepted. Gradation 2 met."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
