      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor. Solver error beyond discretization is addressed through code verification activities.",
      "rationale": "At Model Risk Level 2, explicit quantification of numerical solver error (beyond discretization and code verification) is not required per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. Code verification (factor assessed separately) provides sufficient coverage. Factor scoped to Gradation 1 (not assessed); acceptable at MRL 2."
    },
    {
