      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for computational hemolysis prediction in this COU. Experimental sample characterization addressed under Test Conditions factor.",
      "rationale": "Formal test sample assessment not required at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for this factor and device class. Sample-to-sample variability of blood analog addressed within Test Conditions factor (viscosity uncertainty ±3%). Gradation 1 acceptable at MRL 2."
