      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2. Equivalency between validation experiment inputs and COU inputs addressed qualitatively under Relevance of Validation Activities factor.",
      "rationale": "Formal equivalency assessment not required at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. Qualitative equivalency argument provided under Relevance of Validation Activities to COU factor, which documents that operating conditions, geometry, and fluid properties are within 5% of COU values. Gradation 1 acceptable at MRL 2."
